                                    <watches>0</watches>
                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12540573" author="jimk" created="Tue, 6 Nov 2007 21:16:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Just remember that the number of requests is per heart-beat interval and is not averaged or accumulated in any way.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Depending on when you look, the rate could either be very high or very low.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We need a better way of doing this, when we get more serious about load balancing.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12540577" author="stack" created="Tue, 6 Nov 2007 21:26:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Let me update the UI so that at least there its explicit that its requests per interval.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12540623" author="stack" created="Tue, 6 Nov 2007 23:31:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Added explaination of requests as part of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-167&quot; title=&quot;[hbase] Simple switch to enable DEBUG level-logging in hbase&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-167&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HADOOP-2074&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.  Resolving as won&apos;t fix (since not really broken).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
